\pard\sb240\sa120\keepn\f0\fs40\b\cf2 7. Collaborative aspect and shared folder\b0\cf1\fs22\par
\pard\sa120\sl276\slmult1\fs22 The tool delivers its full value when shared and when every actor works from the same reference folder.\par
\pard\sb200\sa100\keepn\f0\fs30\b\cf2 7.1 Suggested layout\b0\cf1\fs22\par
\pard\sa60\sl240\slmult1\li360\f1\fs20\cf4 \\\\share\\lucie\\\line +-- _config\\\line |   +-- exclusion.xlsx\line |   +-- rules.xml\line |   +-- pmd_ruleset.xml\line +-- squad-alpha\\\line |   +-- 2026-04-11\\\line |   |   +-- index.html\line |   |   +-- excel\\...\line |   |   +-- word\\data_dictionary.docx\line |   |   +-- word\\summary.docx\line |   +-- 2026-04-25\\\line +-- squad-beta\\\line +-- design-review\\\line     +-- 2026-04-15-minutes.docx\line     +-- 2026-04-29-minutes.docx\line \f0\fs22\cf1\par
\pard\sb200\sa100\keepn\f0\fs30\b\cf2 7.2 Collaborative benefits\b0\cf1\fs22\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa80\sl276\slmult1\fs22 \bullet\tab Single view: everyone reads the same data and the same rules.\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa80\sl276\slmult1\fs22 \bullet\tab Capitalisation: the generation history works as the collective memory of the org.\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa80\sl276\slmult1\fs22 \bullet\tab Comparison: Tech Leads can compare their Squad with others on the same basis.\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa80\sl276\slmult1\fs22 \bullet\tab Traceable decisions: Design Review minutes refer to rule identifiers, making arbitrations replayable.\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa80\sl276\slmult1\fs22 \bullet\tab Easier communication: the Word documents can be shared with non-technical stakeholders (Product Owners, Architects, Sponsors).\par
\pard\sa160\sb160\li360\ri360\b\cf4\fs24 [DIAGRAM PLACEHOLDER 3: Collaborative view - insert here the PNG or PDF export of collaboration_overview.drawio.]\b0\cf1\fs22\par
\pard\sb240\sa120\keepn\f0\fs40\b\cf2 8. Best practices\b0\cf1\fs22\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa80\sl276\slmult1\fs22 \bullet\tab Refresh the docs after each major change (new module, object refactor, important batch).\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa80\sl276\slmult1\fs22 \bullet\tab Version the shared configuration (exclusion.xlsx, rules.xml, pmd_ruleset.xml).\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa80\sl276\slmult1\fs22 \bullet\tab Name the generation subfolders with an ISO date YYYY-MM-DD to ease sorting.\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa80\sl276\slmult1\fs22 \bullet\tab Limit the use of the exclusion file: it must reflect architecture decisions, not hide problems.\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa80\sl276\slmult1\fs22 \bullet\tab Agree on scoring weights upfront: a score is only meaningful against a shared reference.\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa80\sl276\slmult1\fs22 \bullet\tab Store Design Review minutes alongside the analysed documentation for traceability.\par
\pard\fi-360\li720\sa80\sl276\slmult1\fs22 \bullet\tab Run a full cycle (generation + Design Review + fix) at least once per release.\par
